 use their beach and facilities, and may ask you to pay in cash -- make sure you use credit card and check how much they're charging you -- they work together to gip you outta your money and keep the cash!Cranes are everywhere in Dubai! It is hard to avoid hearing or seeing construction. Everything is man-made. For vacation, I would recommend visiting Dubai in 6-8 years when things are a lot more developed and settled.Overall, a wonderful and comfortable stay at the Fairmont. Dubai is a place I'd recommend visiting in a couple years, not now when everything is still under construction.	
